{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1275349, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 251527, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果不是热爱科研，博士容易毕不了业…博士和硕士不一样，有硬性毕业要求的", "timestamp": 1615959684, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1275351, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 251527, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 什么毕业要求？论文发表嘛", "timestamp": 1615959723, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1275377, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 251527, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 是的…而且这个东西非常玄学，有比较大的运气成分。和你的导师水平、研究方向、实验设备（某些做AI的组卡都不够用怎么搞）、审稿人口味等都有很大关系", "timestamp": 1615960034, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1275443, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 251527, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我觉得不划算，读博太恶心了", "timestamp": 1615960717, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1275473, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 251527, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不划算。但就生医药博士来说，读博需要经历很痛苦的科研挣扎过程，对科研完全没兴趣大概率quit转硕，遇到恶心的老板想走都难。有这个功夫做点自己喜欢的擅长的多好", "timestamp": 1615961060, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1281467, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 251527, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "千万别", "timestamp": 1616028134, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 7, "pid": 251527, "reply": 6, "tag": null, "text": "对科研无感，为了学历读博划算吗", "timestamp": 1615959545, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1616028131, "url": "", "vote": {}}}